{"type": "article", "id": 22746, "title": "北欧式咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140842xqBF9IagMljueKVZ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典女设计师 Monica Förster 为家具品牌 Erik Jørgensen 设计的咖啡桌，与她一年前设计的沙发是配套的，因而结构类似。她使用细木腿做结构，微微叉开，简洁优雅。桌腿和桌面有一根横梁似的木条连接，露出来圆形截面，增加了温和的性格。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140841v9zK5bxFCmLB1kUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140841xeCBwXbk8OJohtV7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140841napW8PjxGisCoBEe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58974359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140842iO5JWX8R1qkCzDbu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}